: 1629, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"the hamstring calm\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once I got that done, I was told I can go to the track and do a warm-up session just to feel out how the leg was feeling.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"a warm-up session\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"the leg\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I came here today after the warm-up session, felt pretty good.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the warm-up session\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The guys knew what I was facing, and still trusted me, and I am so happy that I am on the podium with them.\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The guys\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am super proud of them, because without them not setting up the race, I would not have been here today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am still in pain.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My hamstring is heavily, heavily strapped, but this is the Olympics final of the 4x100, and the guys needed me.\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My hamstring\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a season's best for the British men's quartet in 37.61, with Canada champions in 37.50.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 223